name: BRADLEY
description:
-DOG COLLECTION- 
.
Introduction:
.
I present this collection of Dogs that I have had to portray. I usually do this type of work so it is a collection that will expand over time. These first three NFTs are a selection of my most interesting works.
.
BRADLEY:
.
It is the last portrait that I had to do and the first painting that I finished in 2022, I loved working on the details of this cute PUG. For now it is one of my favorites and that is why it is the Special piece of this collection.
.
